data.description: Welcome home!!  Enjoy this lovely home sitting on a very private lot just over one acre.  This home has all the room you need with a two story foyer, formal living room/office.  It features a large formal dining room right off the gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Enjoy the open floor plan with a view to the family room from the kitchen or breakfast room.  It also features a large owner's suite with a double vanity and large jet tub and separate shower. The secondary bedrooms upstairs are well sized with a large bedroom or bonus room.
